# AI Prompt Engineering Consultant - Environment Variables
# 僅包含敏感資訊 (Secrets Only)
# 複製此文件為 .env 並填入真實值 (Copy this file to .env and fill in real values)

# ============================================
# AWS Bedrock (Claude) - Secrets
# ============================================
# 從 AWS Console 獲取 (Get from AWS Console)
# https://console.aws.amazon.com/iam/
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_aws_access_key_here
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_aws_secret_key_here

# ============================================
# Google Gemini API - Secrets
# ============================================
# 從 Google AI Studio 獲取 (Get from Google AI Studio)
# https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ============================================
# Google Vertex AI - Secrets
# ============================================
# Google Cloud 專案 ID (可在 config.yaml 中設定或在此覆蓋)
# GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT=your-project-id

# Google Cloud 服務帳戶金鑰文件路徑
# 從 Google Cloud Console 下載 (Download from Google Cloud Console)
# https://console.cloud.google.com/iam-admin/serviceaccounts
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/service-account-key.json

# ============================================
# OpenAI - Secrets
# ============================================
# 從 OpenAI Platform 獲取 (Get from OpenAI Platform)
# https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# ============================================
# 注意事項 (Notes)
# ============================================
# 1. 此文件包含敏感資訊，絕不要提交到 Git
#    This file contains secrets, NEVER commit to Git
#
# 2. 本地開發時，複製此文件為 .env 並填入真實值
#    For local development, copy this file to .env and fill in real values
#
# 3. 生產環境建議使用更安全的方式管理密鑰（如 AWS Secrets Manager, Google Secret Manager）
#    For production, use secure secret management (e.g., AWS Secrets Manager, Google Secret Manager)
#
# 4. 環境變數優先級：環境變數 > .env 文件 > config.yaml
#    Priority: Environment Variables > .env file > config.yaml
